headline: Northrop Wins $97.5M Deal to Support F-35 APG-85 Radar System
summary: NOC lands a $97.5 million deal for the F-35 combat aircraft's APG-85 radar. The company has decade-long expertise in advanced airborne radar systems.

headline: Boeing Secures a $198M Contract to Support F/A-18 Block II Aircraft
summary: BA lands a $198M Navy contract to extend F/A-18 Block II Super Hornet lifespan and add Block III avionics upgrades by 2027.
